    "green_bar_visual_discrepancies": "Multiple screenshots show the green charge bar NOT reaching the charge limit dot position despite 'Charging Complete' status. Most extreme: IMG_1391-1396 where bar is essentially empty (red/tiny) but car reports charging complete.",
    "red_cable_anomaly": "IMG_1597-1604 show the charge cable rendered in RED instead of green, suggesting a charging fault or error state. The car shows 0 kW, 0/40A, 0V despite being plugged in and saying 'Charging'.",
    "pattern": "The BMS consistently reports 'Charging Complete' well below the set charge limit. The discrepancy ranges from 12% (78% actual vs 90% limit) to 99% (2 mi/~1% actual vs 100% limit). Cold battery exacerbates the issue but it occurs in warm conditions too."
  },
